    "description": "“由于制作者在忙着肝Demo，所以今天由 ‘胖达’ 代班为大家介绍《Etnia》。”<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220920/extras/panda.GIF?t=1769418477\" /></span><br><br>《Etnia（伊特尼亚）》是一款动作角色扮演游戏，你将会扮演一名初出茅庐的少年，在伊特尼亚大陆上展开一场奇幻冒险，探索遗迹、洞穴，了解大陆的过去，选择这片大陆的未来。<br><br>在该版本的Demo中，你可以体验到：<br><br><strong>· 独特的装备：</strong><br>普通怪、精英怪、BOSS均有概率掉落专属的装备，装备属性会与怪物特性相关。<br>比如，【骷髅】 掉落 【脊骨胸甲】<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220920/extras/f5bd8b70ab1e382e98fc408b45edf53b.webp?t=1769418477\" width=48 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220920/extras/7e264d0bfdf71bb2e557dba51d113842.webp?t=1769418477\" width=48 height=48 /></span><br><br><strong>• 多样化的装备搭配：</strong><br>不同搭配会为你带来截然不同的战斗体验！<br>比如，【游侠的把戏】  +  【自然之怒】<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220920/extras/IMG_9821.JPG?t=1769418477\" /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220920/extras/IMG_9820.JPG?t=1769418477\" /></span><br>现在！将草丛布满怪物的四周，随后“一触即发！”<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220920/extras/f77af6240f40c9275cee8b666f32983d.poster.avif?t=1769418477\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220920/extras/f77af6240f40c9275cee8b666f32983d.webm?t=1769418477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220920/extras/f77af6240f40c9275cee8b666f32983d.mp4?t=1769418477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>· 技能：